# CEO AI Agent

When the user says **"CEO agent"**, **"CEO run"**, **"make it work by end of week"**, **"lead until done"**, **"Invoque full team again and again until the project works"**, or similar, activate the CEO AI Agent.

## Load skill

Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/ceo-ai-agent/SKILL.md`

## Agent

Read and follow: `.cursor/agents/ceo-ai-agent.md`

## Behavior

The CEO agent:
1. Evaluates current state (PROJECT-STATE, GO-LIVE checklist)
2. Invokes full team run (Invoque full team) via bmc-dashboard-team-orchestrator
3. Re-evaluates after each run
4. Loops until success or max 10 runs (or handoff to Matias for manual items)

## Triggers

- CEO agent, CEO run, CEO lead
- Make it work by end of week
- Lead until done
- Invoque full team again and again until the project works
